data.title: FMU Releases Spring 2024 Semester President’s, Dean’s Lists
data.text:
Francis Marion University named 440 full-time students and 47 part-time students to its President’s List for the Spring 2024 semester. In addition, 461 full-time students and 52 part-time students made the Dean’s List for the spring semester.

Students named to the President’s List have earned a GPA of 3.75 or higher for the semester. Dean’s List students have earned a GPA between 3.25 and 3.749 for the semester.

A complete listing of the students follows:
